<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classvigra_1_1BasicImage" kindref="compound" tooltip="Fundamental class template for images.">vigra::FImage</ref><sp/>fimage(width,<sp/>height);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">...</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">vigra::FindMinMax&lt;</highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">float</highlight><highlight class="normal">&gt;<sp/>minmax;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="group__InspectAlgo_1gaa055bcaf71c209fdeb006fe3e44b0452" kindref="member" tooltip="Apply read-only functor to every pixel in the image.">vigra::inspectImage</ref>(srcImageRange(fimage),<sp/>minmax);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
